[129.059199, "o", "    for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>         c[i] = a->diag_inv[i] * b[i];\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h"]
[129.060194, "o", ">     }\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> }\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> EOF\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
